'''科比·奥乌苏·阿瑟''' （{{lang-en|'''Koby Owusu Arthur'''}}；{{bd|1996年|1月31日}}）是一位[[加納|加納]]藉足球運動員，在場上的位置是中場。他現在效力於[[英格蘭足球全國聯賽_(第一級)|英格蘭足球全國聯]]球會[[马科斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|马科斯菲尔德]]。

==早年==
阿瑟生於加納[[库马西|库马西]]<ref name=SquadNo>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/squad-number-for-koby-665006.aspx |title=Squad number for Koby |first=Andy |last=Walker |publisher=Birmingham City F.C |date=19 February 2013 |accessdate=2 April 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130225014629/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/squad-number-for-koby-665006.aspx |archivedate=2013年2月25日 }}</ref>，搬到英格蘭後加入[[英格蘭足球南部聯賽|南部聯賽]]球會[[伍德福德聯足球會|伍德福德聯]]的青訓系統<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.daventryexpress.co.uk/sport/reds-see-youth-policy-successes-1-3855028 |title=Reds see youth policy successes |work=Daventry Express |date=20 May 2012 |accessdate=2 April 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923212937/http://www.daventryexpress.co.uk/sport/reds-see-youth-policy-successes-1-3855028 |archive-date=2015-09-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，在2012年被伯明翰的球探發現，於是在16歲一年他加入伯明翰青年學院<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/koby-arthur-set-sign-first-1877363 |title=Blues hoping to get Koby Arthur signing on dotted line |first=Colin |last=Tattum |work=Birmingham Mail |date=23 March 2013 |accessdate=2 April 2013 |archive-date=2019-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208211508/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/koby-arthur-set-sign-first-1877363 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Lowdown>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/blues-under-21development-squad-coach-richard-1340283 |title=Lowdown on new Blues prospect Koby Arthur |first=Colin |last=Tattum |work=Birmingham Mail |date=22 February 2013 |accessdate=2 April 2013 |archive-date=2019-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207071416/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/blues-under-21development-squad-coach-richard-1340283 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在U18和預備隊上場比賽。

==球會生涯==
===伯明翰城===
2013年4月1日，阿瑟簽下為期兩年的職業合約<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/pro-deal-for-koby-745030.aspx |title=Pro deal for Koby |first=Andy |last=Walker |publisher=Birmingham City F.C |date=1 April 2013 |accessdate=2 April 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130404030327/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/pro-deal-for-koby-745030.aspx |archivedate=2013年4月4日 }}</ref>，當天他亦首次在職業聯賽上場參加對[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]的賽事，在78分鐘入替[[米切·漢科斯|米切·漢科斯]]，最終以3-2戰敗完場<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/incoming/birmingham-city-2-wolves-3-2498558 |title=Birmingham City 2 Wolves 3 |first=Colin |last=Tattum |work=Birmingham Mail |date=2 April 2013 |accessdate=2 April 2013 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126164726/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/incoming/birmingham-city-2-wolves-3-2498558 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。季後他當選為青年學院年度最佳球員<ref name=AcademyPotY>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/curtis-davies-named-birmingham-city-3412203 |title=Curtis Davies named Birmingham City Player of the Season |author=Tattum, Colin |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=5 May 2013 |accessdate=6 May 2013 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226082615/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/curtis-davies-named-birmingham-city-3412203 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年8月6日[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]第一輪賽事中，他首次以先發身份上場比賽，結果球會在加時以3-2[[普利茅斯足球俱乐部|普利茅斯]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/fixtures-results/match-report/?matchid=3630015&tcmuri=920981 |title=Match report: Birmingham 3–2 Plymouth |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=6 August 2013 |accessdate=7 August 2013 |archive-date=2015-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150713103622/http://www.bcfc.com/fixtures-results/match-report/?matchid=3630015&tcmuri=920981 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，數天後他亦在新球季首次上場參加對[[布莱顿足球俱乐部|布莱顿]]的賽事<ref name=sb1314>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=69772&season_id=143 |title=Games played by Koby Arthur in 2013/2014 |work=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=27 April 2014 |archive-date=2019-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207071659/https://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=69772&season_id=143 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===外借===
2014年3月21日，阿瑟被外借到[[英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽|全國聯]]球會[[林肯城足球俱乐部|林肯城]]至季末<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.redimps.co.uk/news/article/140321-koby-arthur-1435112.aspx |title=Blues' teenager joins on youth loan |publisher=Lincoln City F.C. |date=21 March 2014 |accessdate=21 March 2014 |archive-date=2016-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160324191519/http://www.redimps.co.uk/news/article/140321-koby-arthur-1435112.aspx |dead-url=no }}<br>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/20140321-koby-arthur-joins-the-imps-1434906.aspx |title=Koby Arthur joins the Imps |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=21 March 2014 |accessdate=21 March 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140323122109/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/20140321-koby-arthur-joins-the-imps-1434906.aspx |archivedate=2014年3月23日 }}</ref>。接著對[[盖茨黑德足球俱乐部|盖茨黑德]]賽事便獲得先發席位上場，但半場球隊收2-0落後時被換出<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.lincolnshireecho.co.uk/Gateshead-3-Lincoln-City-1-Match-report/story-20842566-detail/story.html |title=Gateshead 3 Lincoln City 1: Match report |first=John |last=Pakey |newspaper=Lincolnshire Echo |date=22 March 2014 |accessdate=23 March 2014 |archive-date=2014-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140323164133/http://www.lincolnshireecho.co.uk/Gateshead-3-Lincoln-City-1-Match-report/story-20842566-detail/story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年7月25日，他被外借到英乙球會[[切尔滕汉姆足球俱乐部|切尔滕汉姆]]六個月<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ctfc.com/news/article/koby-arthur-loan-1781057.aspx |title=Koby Arthur arrives on loan |publisher=Cheltenham Town F.C. |date=25 July 2014 |accessdate=25 July 2014 |archive-date=2016-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160331121405/http://www.ctfc.com/news/article/koby-arthur-loan-1781057.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他在新球會第二場賽事便取我首顆職業進球，他在84分鐘的進球使球隊最終以2-1擊敗[[艾宁顿斯坦利足球俱乐部|艾宁顿斯坦利]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.gloucestershireecho.co.uk/Cheltenham-Town-2-Accrington-Stanley-1-Jon-Palmer/story-22758744-detail/story.html |title=Cheltenham Town 2 Accrington Stanley 1 |first=Jon |last=Palmer |newspaper=Gloucestershire Echo |date=17 August 2014 |accessdate=17 August 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819084700/http://www.gloucestershireecho.co.uk/Cheltenham-Town-2-Accrington-Stanley-1-Jon-Palmer/story-22758744-detail/story.html |archivedate=2014年8月19日 }}</ref>。一星期後對[[特兰米尔流浪者足球俱乐部|特兰米尔流浪者]]的比賽又取得進球，助球隊以3-2反勝<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/live/match/314918/report |title=Cheltenham down Tranmere |publisher=Sky Sports |date=23 August 2014 |accessdate=23 August 2014 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006083328/http://www1.skysports.com/football/live/match/314918/report |dead-url=no }}</ref>。接著對[[哈特尔普尔联足球俱乐部|哈特尔普尔联]]的賽時，他在90分補打進一頭球，使他有「超級替補」的稱呼<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.gloucestershireecho.co.uk/Cheltenham-Town-v-Hartlepool-United-Match-day/story-22849069-detail/story.html |title=Cheltenham Town v Hartlepool United: Match day LIVE and whistle report |first=Jon |last=Palmer |newspaper=Gloucestershire Echo |date=29 August 2014 |accessdate=3 September 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140831111216/http://www.gloucestershireecho.co.uk/Cheltenham-Town-v-Hartlepool-United-Match-day/story-22849069-detail/story.html |archivedate=2014年8月31日 }}</ref>。他在[[英格蘭聯賽錦標|英格蘭聯賽錦標]]第一輪賽事先發上場並打進球隊第二球，使球隊得以晉級至第二輪<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.gloucestershireecho.co.uk/Cheltenham-Town-v-Oxford-United-Match-night-LIVE/story-22864166-detail/story.html |title=Cheltenham Town v Hartlepool United: Match day LIVE and whistle report |first=Jon |last=Palmer |newspaper=Gloucestershire Echo |date=2 September 2014 |accessdate=3 September 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140905141802/http://www.gloucestershireecho.co.uk/Cheltenham-Town-v-Oxford-United-Match-night-LIVE/story-22864166-detail/story.html |archivedate=2014年9月5日 }}</ref>。9月13日以1-0不敵[[卢顿足球俱乐部|卢顿]]的賽事<ref name=sb1415>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=69772&season_id=144 |title=Games played by Koby Arthur in 2014/2015 |work=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=3 January 2015 |archive-date=2019-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207085155/https://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=69772&season_id=144 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他首次在聯賽先發上場。翌日阿瑟被伯明翰召回<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-teenage-attacker-koby-7770635 |title=Teenage attacker Koby Arthur recalled from loan |last=Tattum |first=Colin |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=14 September 2014 |accessdate=14 September 2014 |archive-date=2019-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207170139/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-teenage-attacker-koby-7770635 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===回到伯明翰===
2014年9月30日伯明翰以3-1擊敗[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|米尔沃尔]]的比賽，阿瑟首次代表伯明翰上場，這場比賽亦是球隊在新球季首場作客勝利<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-boss-lee-clark-7860953 |title=Birmingham City boss Lee Clark reflects on victory over Millwall |last=Tattum |first=Colin |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=1 October 2014 |accessdate=1 October 2014 |archive-date=2019-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208171706/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-boss-lee-clark-7860953 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
